posting_body: ['Martingale Apartments', 'Located at: 8675', 'Litt Dr SE Lacey, WA 98516', 'Featured unit: 2 bed | 2 bath | 1045 sq ft', 'Prices start at: $2285 - $2310/month', 'Call Today!', 'show contact info', 'With rich roots in horse racing, Lacey was home to the first racing track west of the Mississippi.', "Today you'll find every convenience nearby, and with numerous lakes and parks, miles of hiking and biking trails, and a 3,700-acre wildlife refuge, we wager you'll discover plenty of opportunities to enjoy all the fresh air.", 'Wonderful Amenities!', '➢ 24/7 Package Lockers', '➢ Carports & Garages*', '➢ Conference Room', '➢ Game Room with Billiards', '➢ Pet Play Area', '➢ Playground', '➢ Pool & Spa', '➢ Private Offices', '➢ 24-Hour Fitness Studio with Protein Shake Machine', '➢ Clubhouse Lounge with Fireplace & Big Screens', '➢ Community Kitchen with Espresso and Coffee Bar', '➢ EV Charging Stations', '➢ Outdoor Lounge with Ping Pong, BBQs & Fireplace', '➢ Package Service', 'Apartment Features!', '➢ Private Patios/Balconies', '➢ Spacious Studio, One- & Two-Bedroom Floor Plans', '➢ Washers & Dryers', '➢ High Ceilings & Oversized Windows*', '➢ Modern, Flat-Panel Cabinets', '➢ Stainless Steel Appliances', '➢ Walk-In Closets', '➢ Wood-Style Plank Flooring', 'show contact info', 'Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Terms:', '3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month', 'Pet Policy:', 'Martingale Apartments is a pet friendly community.', 'We allow two (2) pets max per household.', '$25/pet monthly pet rent per pet.', '$250 refundable deposit per pet, $250 non-refundable fee per pet.', 'Breed Restrictions Apply.', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '84E9BCA314D047']
